OL,3,CSchool children get free heart scans
OL,4,Cin memory of former pupil
OL,6,FA woman from Jordanstown has raised
OL,7,Fenough money to give 100 school
OL,8,Fchildren a heart scan in memory of her
OL,9,Fbrother.
OL,11,FAmy Adair-McCourt lost her brother,
OL,12,FNicky, when he was just 37-years-old
OL,13,Fto Sudden Adult Death Syndrome,
OL,14,Fotherwise known as SADS.
OL,16,FNicky had just moved back to Northern
OL,17,FIreland with his pregnant wife and one-
OL,18,Fyear-old child.
