OL,6,FHis death rocked the whole family but
OL,7,Fin her grief, Amy began fundraising
OL,8,Ffor CRY, a charity which helps those
OL,9,Fwho have lost someone to a sudden
OL,10,Fcardiac death.
OL,12,FThe charity also provides mobile heart-
OL,13,Fscreening clinics.
OL,15,FThe heart scan costs #60 per adult,
OL,16,Ftotalling to #6,000 to give 100 pupils
OL,17,Fthe screening.
