OL,3,CSchool children get free heart scans
OL,4,Cin memory of former pupil
OL,6,F"Grief is hard and it's sad and it
OL,7,Falways will be sad, but selfishly I
OL,8,Fwanted something to channel that
OL,9,Fsadness and grief into," said Amy.
OL,11,F"I like to fundraise when I can and
OL,12,Fthere was a lot of thought around what
OL,13,Fthis fundraising money should go into
OL,14,Fand it came down to how can we help
OL,15,Fprevent this (SADS) in any way we can.
OL,17,F"How can I prevent another family from
OL,18,Fhaving to go through what we've gone
OL,19,Fthrough and for something positive to
OL,20,Fcome out of something so horrendous."
