OL,3,CSchool children get free heart scans
OL,4,Cin memory of former pupil
OL,6,FSpeaking to some of the pupils after
OL,7,Ftheir screening, all fed back that it
OL,8,Fwas quick, painless and gave them a
OL,9,Fsense of reassurance going forward.
OL,11,FAn ECG is taken before electrodes are
OL,12,Fplaced on the chest and ankles to
OL,13,Fmeasure the heart's electrical
OL,14,Fimpulses.
OL,16,FIf an anomaly is found by a
OL,17,Fspecialist, a follow-up letter will be
OL,18,Fsent out in the post referring them
OL,19,Ffor further investigation.
