OL,6,FAround 12 otherwise healthy young
OL,7,Fadults die every week from an
OL,8,Fundiagnosed heart anomaly in the UK.
OL,10,FBy screening, issues can be flagged
OL,11,Fearly and preventative measures can be
OL,12,Fput in place to save lives.
OL,14,FAmy hopes other schools will be
OL,15,Finspired to roll out similar heart
OL,16,Fscreening tests in the hopes that more
OL,17,Fyoung lives are saved.
